      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start, quite atmospheric. Now, to make the tension even more specific, I need to start introducing the people who live there. I don't want to name specific names yet, but can you describe the types of people hanging out on the corners or walking through these alleys? Instead of just \"people,\" give me some descriptions of their appearance, what they're wearing, and the \"vibe\" they give off to a visitor—you know, to really cement that sense of danger and social decline.",
